      	<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn">

      		<p>
      			<lb n="1"/>kō-vicaiya-ciṅkaviṇṇa-parumaṟkup pattoṉpa<choice><sic>t</sic><corr>tt</corr></choice>-āvatu
      		</p>

      		<p>
      			<lb n="2"/>mēl-veṇṇāṭṭuc ciṟuppāḻ Āḷum pālāyiriyaru makkaḷ
      			<lb n="3"/>ciṟuppaṭuvāṉāru karuṅkālippāṭit toṟuk koḷap pūcal ceṉṟu
      			<lb n="4"/>puyanāṭṭup pila<unclear>yācata</unclear>ṅkaḷ Eṟintu paṭṭāṉ kal
      		</p>

      	</div>

